name: I Don't Know you
description:
HTML5 browser game made in Twine.  Submission for WJG Narrative Game Jam #1. 

There's a cocoon dangling from your ceiling, and a song that you created. Listen to it the way it was supposed to be felt.

Note: Audio issues may occur when attempting to undo choices or open Saves. Simply save your game and Restart before opening the save file to fix the problem. Thank you for playing!
